Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃金北海道小劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿伊努的神謠中有段關於山鷸的卡姆依的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講的是它與黑啄木鳥的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,標題是山鷸的戀愛占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛情故事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心上人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得我好心焦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去山林裡找你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林中的茖蔥長得脆嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它來算一算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心上人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我摘這茖蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以連根拔起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著我伸手去摘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到拔到中途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只把客蔥葉拔了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我氣不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉起葉子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往天上扔去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接著往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了好遠好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次看到了大百合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心上人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我摘這大百合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以連根拔起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著我伸手去摘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只聽砰地一聲  大百合被完整地拔了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心裡很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來發現心上人一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正笑咪咪地看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我們牽著手走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是山鷸的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可愛的故事呀
